<script type="text/javascript">
function togPhase(n) {
	var e = document.getElementById('phasehint' + n);
	e.style.display = e.style.display == 'none' ? 'block' : 'none';
}
function togAllPhases(display) {
	for (var i = 1; i <= 50; i++) {
		var e = document.getElementById('phasehint' + i);
		if (!e) break;
		e.style.display = display;
	}
}
function addHint(n) {
	var e = document.getElementById('phase');
	for (var i = 0; i < e.childNodes.length; i++) {
		e.childNodes[i].selected = e.childNodes[i].value == n ? 'selected' : '';
	}
	e = document.getElementById('text');
	e.focus();
	e.select();
}
</script>

<div class="mm white">
This quest <span class="blue">[<span class="yellow">1396</span>]</span> is called '<span class="yellow">Zombie Master</span>',<br/>
for Adventurers levels <span class="yellow">120</span> to <span class="yellow">180</span>.<br />


<span class="hg"><a href="/npc/3438">Lord Vashir</a> [<a href="/area/61">The Towne of New Rigel</a>] is the master in charge of this quest.</span><br />

On your way into Lord Vashir's throne room, a hooded figure jumps from<br />
the shadows and stops you.  Before you can draw your weapon, he says, "Don't<br />
attack!  I'm a loyal servant of Lord Vashir.  He has a secret mission for<br />
you.  It is so controversial that he cannot deliver its details in person. <br />
Lord Vashir is trying to unravel the mysteries of Avarice, but his<br />
unconventional approach involves creating zombies so he can find better<br />
means of destroying them.  Yes, I know it is horrible, but the evil there<br />
must be dealt with.  You may want to purify yourself afterwards, and pray<br />
that a greater good can come out of Lord Vashir's plan."<br />

<span class="hy">Upon successful completion of this quest you can receive:</span><br />

<span class="hm">*</span>Up to <span class="yellow">55</span> quest points, <span class="yellow">5</span> practice points, <span class="yellow">30,000</span> experience points,<br/>
&nbsp;<span class="yellow">0</span> build points, <span class="yellow">0</span> piety, and <span class="yellow">10,000</span> gold pieces.<br />


You have <span class="yellow">300</span> minutes remaining to complete this quest.<br />

Zombie Master consists of:<br />


	<div class="phase" id="phase1">


		<a class="hints" href="javascript:togPhase(1);">Phase 1</a>: Journey to <a href="/room/19382">Corpse Preparation Room #8</a>. 		
		<div class="phasehints" id="phasehint1" style="display: none;">

<div class="phaseinforoom">in <a href="/area/67">Towne of Rune</a>.</div>


			<div class="phasehint">
				Dunbar Morgue in Rune...last south on the eastern side				&mdash;
				Drahylin							</div>


		</div>
	</div>


	<div class="phase" id="phase2">


		<a class="hints" href="javascript:togPhase(2);">Phase 2</a>: Defeat <a href="/npc/122">A zombie</a>. 		
		<div class="phasehints" id="phasehint2" style="display: none;">

<div class="phaseinfomob">in <a href="/room/2442">Burial Vaults</a>, <a href="/area/35">Lowangen</a>.</div>


